 ![Prince William admiring his wife Kate Middleton while she's in conversation.](https://a57.foxnews.com/static.foxnews.com/foxnews.com/content/uploads/2026/01/1200/675/prince-william-kate-middleton-2026.jpg?ve=1&tl=1)

