"Andrew was in Bahrain for investment schemes and networking projects," Fordwich said. "Qatar and [Saudi Arabia](https://www.foxnews.com/category/world/world-regions/saudi-arabia) are other possibilities."

Royal biographer Andrew Lownie also told People magazine that a move to the Middle East could be possible for the late queen’s favored son.

 ![Queen Elizabeth wearing a hunter green coat dress with a matching hat being accompanied by Prince Andrew in a dark suit.](https://a57.foxnews.com/static.foxnews.com/foxnews.com/content/uploads/2025/08/1200/675/queen-elizabeth-prince-andrew-church-outing.jpg?ve=1&tl=1)

