Chard previously told Fox News Digital that William [and his wife Kate Middleton](https://www.foxnews.com/category/world/personalities/kate) are quietly enforcing a stricter "zero-tolerance" approach within the monarchy following Andrew’s scandals. Their approach to the monarchy’s future began before Andrew was stripped of his title.

 ![Prince William and Kate Middleton in royal robes smiling at each other.](https://a57.foxnews.com/static.foxnews.com/foxnews.com/content/uploads/2025/11/1200/675/prince-william-kate-middleton-king-charles-coronation-celebration.jpg?ve=1&tl=1)

